sequenceDiagram
  participant Controller
  participant AuditLogAspect
  participant UseCase
  participant AuditLogRepository

  Controller->>AuditLogAspect: invoke use case method [AOP intercept]
  AuditLogAspect->>UseCase: proceed() [executes original method]
  UseCase-->>AuditLogAspect: result
  AuditLogAspect->>AuditLogAspect: buildAuditLog(entityName, action, user, details)
  AuditLogAspect->>AuditLogRepository: save(auditLog)
  Note over AuditLogRepository: Persistit a MongoDB
  AuditLogRepository-->>AuditLogAspect: saved
  AuditLogAspect-->>Controller: result (transparent)
